@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/ords/infoplan/facturacion/api/v1/aprobaciones-rechazos

### 1) Oficial lookup
GET {{baseUrl}}/oficiales/101
Accept: application/json

### 2) Search by date range (all filters null)
POST {{baseUrl}}/transacciones/search
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "fec_ini": "2026-06-01",
  "fec_fin": "2026-06-30",
  "cliente": null,
  "oficial": null,
  "gerente": null,
  "intermediario": null
}

### 3) Search by oficial
POST {{baseUrl}}/transacciones/search
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "fec_ini": "2026-06-01",
  "fec_fin": "2026-06-30",
  "cliente": null,
  "oficial": 101,
  "gerente": null,
  "intermediario": null
}

### 4) Mark all selections
POST {{baseUrl}}/transacciones/seleccion/M
Accept: application/json

### 5) Generate OLE mock export payload
POST {{baseUrl}}/exportaciones/ole
Accept: application/json

### 6) Unmark all selections
POST {{baseUrl}}/transacciones/seleccion/D
Accept: application/json

### 7) Generate Jasper mock export payload
POST {{baseUrl}}/exportaciones/jasper
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "fec_ini": "2026-06-01",
  "fec_fin": "2026-06-30"
}
